sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant UI as React UI
  participant API as Express API
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  User->>UI: Submit login form
  UI->>API: POST /auth/login (credentials)
  API->>DB: SELECT user + org info
  DB-->>API: user row
  API->>API: Verify password + sign JWT
  API-->>UI: 200 {token, profile}
  UI->>UI: Persist token + profile
  UI-->>User: Route by role
